Key Match Events: The Thunder forced 19 turnovers, leading to 17 fast break points and 13 total points off turnovers.
Norman Powell and Amir Coffey were the primary victims to the Thunder defense, with Powell coughing the ball up six times and Coffey four times.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The team's starting five dominated the court, averaging a plus-minus of plus-23.4 throughout its core.
The Thunder outscored the Clippers 58-32 in the paint.
Others: The Thunder awaits the return of Chet Holmgren.
The team will face the New York Knicks at home on Friday.
